# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:25
translate chinese u19a2s7a_d7391ca9:

    # "We walk until the sun begins to set and it's time to set up camp once again."
    "我们一直走，直到太阳开始西沉，又到了搭帐篷的时候。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:28
translate chinese u19a2s7a_6347fb4c:

    # mc "You say you are from another world, where there is another me?"
    mc "你说你来自另一个世界，那里还有另一个我？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:29
translate chinese u19a2s7a_ba87bb2f:

    # pc "Yeah, I am."
    pc "是的，我来自那里。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:30
translate chinese u19a2s7a_2aa5ee09:

    # mc "What is she like? Is she a dancer as well?"
    mc "她是什么样的人？她也是个舞者吗？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:31
translate chinese u19a2s7a_74677430:

    # pc "She is, actually. She loves to dance."
    pc "其实是。她非常喜欢跳舞。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:32
translate chinese u19a2s7a_b815dc04:

    # pc "She's very sweet and kind and always trying to please."
    pc "她很温柔善良，总是想讨好别人。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:33
translate chinese u19a2s7a_9ee66c04:

    # pc "She's a little too worried about pleasing everybody else, and doing what everybody else wants her to do..."
    pc "她太在意取悦所有人，总是做别人希望她做的事……"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:34
translate chinese u19a2s7a_70ebbfb3:

    # pc "... instead of focusing on what she wants to do."
    pc "……而不是专注于自己想做的事。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:36
translate chinese u19a2s7a_8eb4e936:

    # mc "Hm, that is not like me at all."
    mc "嗯，那完全不像我。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:37
translate chinese u19a2s7a_2c7a1ece:

    # mc "I always do what I want to do. I am free. Nobody tells Mi-Cha what to do... unless I want them to."
    mc "我总是做我想做的事。我是自由的。没人能命令米查做什么……除非是我愿意让他们这么做。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:39
translate chinese u19a2s7a_42ed4bba:

    # mc "You have to help this other me see that. She is free to do whatever she wants."
    mc "你得帮帮那个“另一个我”，让她明白这一点。她完全可以随心所欲。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:40
translate chinese u19a2s7a_078d69a7:

    # pc "I've been trying."
    pc "我一直在努力。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:44
translate chinese u19a2s7a_35550ef3:

    # cw "I lost my freedom for a long time. It's an awful feeling."
    cw "我很久以前就失去了自由。那种感觉糟透了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:45
translate chinese u19a2s7a_2d600ef3:

    # cw "Everybody should be free to make their own decisions and do what they want with their lives."
    cw "每个人都应该有自由去做出自己的决定，按照自己的意愿生活。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:46
translate chinese u19a2s7a_fcf340b6:

    # mc "I agree."
    mc "我同意。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:49
translate chinese u19a2s7a_45de856f:

    # sg "Why would you care what anybody else thinks? They aren't living your life."
    sg "你为什么要介意别人怎么想？他们又不是在过你的生活。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:50
translate chinese u19a2s7a_8ef70686:

    # sg "Just live it however makes you the happiest, I think."
    sg "我觉得，只要活得让你最开心就好。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:51
translate chinese u19a2s7a_7db64ce6:

    # sg "You only get one, and it's not very long."
    sg "人生只有一次，而且并不长。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:52
translate chinese u19a2s7a_fcf340b6_1:

    # mc "I agree."
    mc "我同意。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:54
translate chinese u19a2s7a_a52521e6:

    # gg "It's important to be whoever you feel like you are meant to be, and nobody else can decide that for you."
    gg "活出你认为自己该有的样子很重要，而这绝非他人能替你决定的。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:55
translate chinese u19a2s7a_fcf340b6_2:

    # mc "I agree."
    mc "我同意。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:57
translate chinese u19a2s7a_54bfdc0f:

    # bn "Sometimes it's difficult to know how to act, and guidance is necessary."
    bn "有时很难知道该怎么做，指导是必要的。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:58
translate chinese u19a2s7a_d671023b:

    # bn "But in the end, everybody should be free to make their own decisions."
    bn "但归根结底，每个人都应该有权自由地做出自己的决定。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:59
translate chinese u19a2s7a_fcf340b6_3:

    # mc "I agree."
    mc "我同意。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:62
translate chinese u19a2s7a_4387a8df:

    # sst "Freedom is the most important thing in the world."
    sst "自由是世界上最重要的东西。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:63
translate chinese u19a2s7a_aa965ea9:

    # sst "Nobody should be allowed to make decisions for you or control your fate!"
    sst "不该允许任何人替你做决定或掌控你的命运！"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:64
translate chinese u19a2s7a_fcf340b6_4:

    # mc "I agree."
    mc "我同意。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:67
translate chinese u19a2s7a_da8c9804:

    # rb "Nobody can tell Reba what to do!"
    rb "谁都别想对丽芭指手画脚！"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:68
translate chinese u19a2s7a_6ac871f9:

    # rb "I'm gonna do whatever the heck I want to, I promise you that!"
    rb "我就要随心所欲地做我想做的事，我向你保证！"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:69
translate chinese u19a2s7a_61a2b50c:

    # mc "That is a good way to live."
    mc "这才是活得自在的方式。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:71
translate chinese u19a2s7a_5706ecf8:

    # mc "I will help you get back to her so that you can help her."
    mc "我会帮你回到她身边，这样你就能帮到她了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:72
translate chinese u19a2s7a_124c4acc:

    # pc "Thanks Mi-Cha. It's definitely nice having you around."
    pc "谢谢米查。有你在身边真好。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:73
translate chinese u19a2s7a_a9a280cd:

    # mc "I am getting tired now. I think I will try to sleep."
    mc "我现在有点累了。我想试着睡会儿。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:74
translate chinese u19a2s7a_d5f58427:

    # pc "Good idea. We should keep a watch overnight though. I can take first watch."
    pc "好主意。不过我们得通宵守夜。我先上第一班。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:77
translate chinese u19a2s7a_d0ff659c:

    # sst "Then I will take second."
    sst "然后我上第二班。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:80
translate chinese u19a2s7a_fd391d92:

    # rb "Then I will take second."
    rb "然后我上第二班。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:83
translate chinese u19a2s7a_fa5c2825:

    # cw "Then I will take second."
    cw "然后我上第二班。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:86
translate chinese u19a2s7a_9a2d0f32:

    # sg "Then me."
    sg "然后我。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:89
translate chinese u19a2s7a_f73f5a01:

    # bn "And I'll be next."
    bn "接着是我。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:92
translate chinese u19a2s7a_ad230cd5:

    # gg "And I'll take the next one."
    gg "然后我上下一班。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:93
translate chinese u19a2s7a_80ca8121:

    # mc "This is a good idea. I will do the last watch then."
    mc "这主意不错。那我就负责最后一班。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:99
translate chinese u19a2s7a_0466c0c7:

    # mc "This is fun. Travelling, talking, sleeping next to the fire."
    mc "真有意思。旅行、聊天、在篝火旁睡觉。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:100
translate chinese u19a2s7a_2ee6cb68:

    # pc "Yeah, it is. If it wasn't for the bandits and the monsters, this place would be pretty nice."
    pc "是啊。要不是有强盗和怪物，这地方还挺不错的。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:101
translate chinese u19a2s7a_68957625:

    # mc "Yes, that is true. I hope it stays peaceful like this."
    mc "是啊，确实如此。希望这里能一直这么和平。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:104
translate chinese u19a2s7a_98dcde50:

    # mc "Good night [pcname]. I am glad that we met."
    mc "晚安[pcname]。很高兴能遇见你。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene7a.rpy:105
translate chinese u19a2s7a_eede79c7:

    # pc "Me too. Good night, Mi-Cha."
    pc "我也是。晚安，米查。"

